commit message: Make all remaining strings in about screen translatable.
Enable fast scroll for list of exchange rates.
Fix pattern to detect wallet import formatted keys for testnet.
Binary and stream input parsers generally don't handle direct transactions.
Prepare separate handling of private keys when parsing input.
Change MIME type for wallet backups because the format changed as well.
Impose a limit of 5 million characters on backup files to read.
Fix backup files do not decrypt using openssl. It expects line lengths of around 80 chars.
Always check network of loaded or restored wallet.
Add recently released fork and reformat the list.
